OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry evening
OL,6,Fwith plenty of evening sunshine with
OL,7,Fclear skies following for many. The
OL,8,Fodd patch of higher cloud, perhaps
OL,9,Fthickest in the east. Staying dry
OL,10,Fovernight with light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FAnother very warm, dry and
OL,13,Flargely sunny day, occasionally hazy
OL,14,Fdue to higher cloud, most likely later
OL,15,Fin the day. Turning breezy especially
OL,16,Falong the English Channel coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
